constraint.SQL:
["(exists(
select 1 from ECIF.lcIB_GS_SBCLSH A, jgcrm.os_wfentry B 
where A.instid = B.id 
and B.state = 4 and A.xmmc = tIB_XMXX_GS.ID
)
OR EXISTS (
select 1 from ecif.lcIB_GS_NHLC A,jgcrm.os_wfentry B
where A.SFYQTSBCLFQYY = 1 and A.BJJG IN (1, 2) and A.INSTID = B.ID and B.STATE = 4 and A.XMMC = tIB_XMXX_GS.ID
))
and not exists(
select 1 from ECIF.lcIB_GS_FKYJHF A, jgcrm.os_wfentry B 
where A.instid = B.id 
and B.state = 1 and A.xmmc = tIB_XMXX_GS.ID 
)
or ID = {1}",[{"expression":"ID","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1},{"expression":"XMMC.ID","scale":0,"length":0,"type":1}]]
